# TDD RED PHASE SKILL

## Goal
Define a single behavior by producing a failing test.

---

## Input
- A requirement or behavior description

---

## Output
- Exactly one failing test
- No production code

---

## Rules
- Write test code only
- Do not write implementation
- Do not refactor
- One test = one behavior

---

## Constraints
- Test must fail for the correct reason
- Test must describe observable behavior, not implementation